Package: axer
Type: Package
Title: Include axe js accessibility tools in web documents produced by R
Version: 0.1.1
Author: Matt Johnson
Maintainer: Matt Johnson <mrjoh3@gmail.com>
Description: The goal of axer is to add [axe](https://github.com/dequelabs/axe-core) 
    accessibility assessment outputs to 
    either a shiny app `qmd` or `Rmd` file. Also to be included are some simple tools 
    to fix common accessibility issues.
